7
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,090
♫  Pretending to be busy every day ♫

8
00:00:31,090 --> 00:00:34,960
♫  But in the end, I could not endure it ♫

9
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:40,570
♫ I want to know what you're up to right now ♫

10
