00:40:12,600 --> 00:40:14,800
I want the lime flavor!

438
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:18,000
Sit.

439
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:24,200
Senior, you really don't have to.

440
00:40:24,200 --> 00:40:27,200
I don't want to bother you.

441
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:30,500
I know time is precious when you're in Year 12.

442
00:40:31,410 --> 00:40:33,650
It's okay, sit down.

443
00:40:36,300 --> 00:40:41,200
By helping you review, I'm also helping myself review.

444
00:40:41,200 --> 00:40:43,000
It works out pretty nicely.

445
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:47,200
The things they test in the unified exams are actually all pretty basic.

446
00:40:47,200 --> 00:40:51,600
Tell me, apart from what we worked on last time,

447
00:40:51,600 --> 00:40:55,900
